  stepNumber: 5
  stepText: "To aim, make a fist with your thumb up.\r\nIn this pose, the striker
    locks and rotates with your wrist movement.\r\nYour wrist band glows green to
    confirm proper aim mode.\r\nYou\u2019ll also see an aim arrow on the striker.
    Rotate your wrist to align this arrow with the glowing guide arrow, then tap
    the thumb.\r\nNow you try it. "
